ow motivate future\nprecision solar system, Vainstein-scale and cosmological-scale studies of Dark\nGravity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 May 2006 14:38:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 12 Jun 2006 15:12:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
